---
import Info from "@/components/Content/Info.astro";
import Prose from "@/components/Content/Prose.astro";
import SidebarPage from "@/layouts/SidebarPage.astro";
---

<SidebarPage
    meta={{
        title: "KAPLAY Guides",
        description: "Learn how to create games with KAPLAY.js through our comprehensive guides and tutorials.",
        keywords: "kaplayjs, guides, documentation",
    }}
    collection="guides"
    category="guides"
>
    <Prose>
        <h1>Welcome to KAPLAY Docs</h1>
        <p>In the KAPLAY Docs you will find guides, resources and all you need to start using the&nbsp;KAPLAY library!</p>
    </Prose>

    <div class="max-w-[50rem]">
        <div class="grid grid-cols-2 bg-base-50 rounded-xl gap-px p-px">
            <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col rounded-xl bg-base-300 p-4 w-full gap-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Getting Started</h2>
                Get started with KAPLAY

                <ul class="list-disc list-inside">
                    <li class="link link-primary link-hover">
                        <a href="/docs/guides/install">Installing</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="link link-primary link-hover">
                        <a href="/docs/guides/starting">Basic Concepts</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="link link-primary link-hover">
                        <a href="/docs/guides/game_objects">Game Objects</a>
                    </li>
                    <li class="link link-primary link-hover">
                        <a href="/docs/guides/components">Components</a>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col rounded-xl bg-base-300 p-4 w-full gap-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold">Create your first game</h2>
                You can start learning KAPLAY.js basics by creating a Chrome Dino-like game

                <a class="link link-hover link-primary" href="/docs/guides/creating_your_first_game">Read "Creating your first game"</a>
            </div>
        </div>

        <Info crew="bean" title="Psst!">
            <p>
                Creating games is an adventure and it doesn't have to be a single-player! Join our
                <a class="link-hover link-primary" href="https://discord.com/invite/aQ6RuQm3TF">Discord Server</a>, where you can share your progress or ask for
                help if you run into any problems.
            </p>
        </Info>

        <div class="grid bg-base-50 rounded-xl gap-px p-px">
            <div class="flex flex-1 flex-col rounded-xl bg-base-300 p-4 w-full gap-2">
                <h2 class="text-xl font-bold flex items-center gap-2"><span class="badge text-white bg-[#7E39E0]">NEW</span>Multiplayer Integration</h2>

                <p>
                    Integrate your KAPLAY games with a flexible and fun multiplayer framework, Colyseus. In our new <a
                        class="link text-[#aa7aee]"
                        href="/docs/guides/how-to-make-a-multiplayer-game-with-colyseus-and-kaplay">Multiplayer Guide</a
                    > you will learn how to from the start to deploying!
                </p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <Prose>Remember that KAPLAY is a new born open source project. This documentation is constantly evolving and advancing :D</Prose>
    </div>
</SidebarPage>
